trans-unit.source: Provides text writer functionality for devices targeted by the XHTML adapter set, including Extensible Hypertext Markup Language (XHTML), XHTML Mobile, and Wireless Markup Language (WML).
trans-unit.target: Gir tekst writer funksjonalitet for enheter som XHTML adapteren sett, inkludert omfattende Hypertext Markup Language (XHTML), XHTML Mobile og trådløst Markup Language (WML).

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om hvordan du utvikler mobile ASP.NET-applikasjoner, kan du se den [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) webområdet.

trans-unit.source: XHTML is an XML-compliant markup that is based on HTML 4.1 and allows you to create Web sites suitable for multiple device types.
trans-unit.target: XHTML er en XML-kompatibel koder som er basert på HTML 4.1 og gjør det mulig å opprette webområder passer for flere enhetstyper.

trans-unit.source: It merges HTML's ease of use with XML's strict element guidelines to produce a markup language with a wide range of format and style options and reduced markup tag ambiguity.
trans-unit.target: Den slår sammen HTMLS brukervennlig med XMLS streng elementet retningslinjene for å generere en markup language med en lang rekke alternativene format og stil og redusert markup koden tvetydighet.

trans-unit.source: This class provides formatting capabilities that ASP.NET server controls use when rendering XHTML content to clients.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen gir formatering funksjoner som ASP.NET serverkontroller brukes ved gjengivelse XHTML innhold til klienter.

trans-unit.source: The XhtmlMobileTextWriter renders markup that meets the standards of three different XHTML doc types: XHTML Basic, which supports limited style and format elements; XHTML Mobile Profile, which supports inline style sheets; and WML 2.0, which is based on XHTML 1.1 and supports cascading style sheets.
trans-unit.target: XhtmlMobileTextWriter gjengir markup som oppfyller standard tre forskjellige typer XHTML doc: XHTML Basic, som støtter begrenset stil elementer. XHTML mobil-profil som støtter innebygd CSS-ark; og WML 2.0, som er basert på XHTML 1.1 og støtter gjennomgripende CSS-ark.

trans-unit.source: This class is used primarily by developers of custom mobile page and control adapters.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes hovedsakelig av utviklerne av egendefinerte Mobil-siden og kontroll kort.

trans-unit.source: The XhtmlMobileTextWriter class can render all HTML elements, attributes, and style attributes, but, unlike the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> class, does not allow title capitalization of these markup elements.
trans-unit.target: Klassen XhtmlMobileTextWriter kan gjengi alle HTML-elementer, attributter, og style attributter, men unlike den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter>klasse, tillater ikke at tittelen store og små bokstaver av disse elementene markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlPageAdapter> instantiates an XhtmlMobileTextWriter and depending on the capabilities of the target device, initializes a number of properties, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SupportsNoWrapStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SuppressNewLine%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.UseDivsForBreaks%2A>, that assist the text writer in rendering the page and its controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlPageAdapter>starter en XhtmlMobileTextWriter og avhengig av funksjoner i målenheten initialiserer en rekke egenskaper, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SupportsNoWrapStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SuppressNewLine%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.UseDivsForBreaks%2A>, som hjelper tekstskriver med gjengivelse siden og tilhørende kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.UseDivsForBreaks%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SuppressNewLine%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.SupportsNoWrapStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlPageAdapter>

trans-unit.source: Your adapter can use a variety of methods to apply styles and control formatting: - <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitStyle%2A>, - <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterLayout%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitLayout%2A>, and - <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterFormat%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitFormat%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Kortet kan bruke en rekke måter å bruke stiler og kontrollere formatering:- <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitStyle%2A>, - <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterLayout%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitLayout%2A>, og - <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterFormat%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitFormat%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitFormat%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterFormat%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitLayout%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterLayout%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.ExitStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.XhtmlAdapters.XhtmlMobileTextWriter.EnterStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter> class, which in turn derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MultiPartWriter> class, and much of its functionality is provided by these base classes.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter>klassen som i sin tur er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MultiPartWriter>klassen, og de fleste funksjonene leveres av disse basisklasser.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MultiPartWriter> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter>

trans-unit.source: You can use the members of this class, and any members it inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter> class, to create custom text writers to use in a custom XHTML page or in class adapters.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke medlemmer av denne klassen, og ingen medlemmer som arver fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter>klassen for å opprette egendefinerte tekst forfattere skal brukes i en egendefinert XHTML-side eller i klassen kort.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Adapters.MobileTextWriter>

trans-unit.source: You can also create new derived classes that override the standard behavior of the XhtmlMobileTextWriter class.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også opprette nye avledede klasser som overstyrer standardvirkemåten for XhtmlMobileTextWriter-klassen.
